Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:40.11,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊擁抱 心靈的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:46.47,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱情燃燒 創造奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.84,0:00:51.84,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就這樣受著傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:58.07,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相發誓過的 遙遠的銀河
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:04.34,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬座的幻想 只有夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:10.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也奪不走 因為是心靈的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:16.29,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 少年都是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.33,0:01:20.47,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 明天的勇士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:27.93,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 就像天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:35.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 現在就展開羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:34.76,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣字幕组&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當邪惡在此世蔓延之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會現身的希望之戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身著星座之聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆發蘊藏在身體中的能量「小宇宙」進行著戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們正是 保護大地上愛與和平的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士光牙尋找雅典娜的旅程還在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯利用擁有強大小宇宙的神秘少女破壞了聖域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧檄的殊死搏鬥 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙等人才成功逃出Palaestra
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:02:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了救出神秘少女 他們決定前往聖域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年們 燃起內心的小宇宙吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本王的偉業正進入新的階段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類未能達成的偉業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.47,0:03:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的希望之塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是真正的巴比倫塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決死之奪還！另一名黃金聖鬥士！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是聖域？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾由十二名黃金聖鬥士守護的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確能感受到強大的小宇宙在釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙又要無腦地衝進去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕隻身一人 我也要去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是說讓你動動腦筋而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊 放馬過來吧 火星士！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幼獅座蒼摩大人來會會你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你玩過頭了 這也太明顯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實有些太囂張了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 都過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的任務只是聲東擊西而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不可以蠻幹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 光牙君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲東擊西？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們三個人在外面吸引敵人的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個就趁機潛入塔裡 救出那個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非去不可！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了 光牙君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能順利嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙還真是一根筋到底啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也一樣 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,營救那個少女是我們唯一的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可要勒好光牙的韁繩 別讓他胡來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形勢不妙的話就趕緊跑路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯和火星士…那群把Palaestra搞得面目全非的傢伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓咱們給他個下馬威吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 龍峰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要藏起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昔人意欲挑戰神祗卻鎩羽而歸的證明 巴比倫塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被奪去了語言 卻絲毫不接受教訓的人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就奪去你們的一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.86,0:09:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒聽到什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴比倫塔終會突破天際
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是光牙 天馬座的光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿…阿…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅…這是你的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前救了我吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次由我 如約來救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然料想你們也是不情不願 但我不會同情你們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切也都是為了保護聖域
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會枉費你們的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我這獅子座黃金聖衣起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座塔到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴比倫塔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瑪爾斯為了實現其野心的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯正在收集小宇宙 籌畫著一件非常可怕的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集小宇宙？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要怎麼收集啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有著儲存聖鬥士們的小宇宙的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼狀況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檄老師 小町 阿爾妮 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著 我現在就救你們出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜大人 請您立刻回到房間去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在您的職責是維持巴比倫塔的穩定運行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儲存光之小宇宙 直到將會到來的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你們把雅典娜大人從核心區域帶出來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:13:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 尤娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮斗！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要跑啊 要趕快救出大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要一邊保護這孩子一邊和黃金聖鬥士戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞了那個柱子 就真能救出大家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情不試試怎麼知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用試！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也知道啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙君 尤娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才想問你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都沒事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上黃金聖鬥士就會追來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會拖住那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家帶著她先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦 我之後一定會趕上的 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜 阿莉雅就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個黃金聖鬥士不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅不在的話 這個塔就沒辦法正常發揮功能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護好阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定可以關係到救出Palaestra的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就拜託你了 尤娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是說 光牙你要一個人獨佔風頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了 我也要留下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想和黃金聖鬥士交一次手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算一個人不行 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個人一起上的話 至少能拖延點時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 盡耍帥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 把你們捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:17:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣 大家都是自己選擇留下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜大人在哪裡 青銅聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是天馬座光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會把阿莉雅交給你們這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要帶回她 就靠你的力量來搶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一決勝負吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:34.25,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁錫尼為古希臘遺址，有著名的獅子門
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是邁錫尼 有著百獸之王般的獠牙 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最為高傲自信的黃金聖鬥士 獅子座的邁錫尼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔？這個小宇宙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼摩！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土遁 蒼牙大狼陣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你使用的招式很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙君！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:19:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然擋住了我的拳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 光牙君…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再問一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜大人在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實力太懸殊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑我們絕對無法勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不能在此…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁錫尼 之後就由我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜呢 沙織小姐在哪 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把沙織小姐還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.74,0:20:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須斷絕掉你的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然還留著如此強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你的光輝即將逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們死在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕的聖鬥士們 由我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤星永恆槍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬流星拳！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.71,0:22:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴比倫塔被強大的小宇宙的爆炸所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜為了守護和光牙的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿莉雅一同脫出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.01,0:22:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅還是第一次看到外界的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.69,0:22:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時追擊他們的白銀聖鬥士出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.03,0:22:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外還有身穿紅黑雙色鎧甲的女火星士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.02,0:22:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 聖鬥士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護阿莉雅！追擊者索尼婭的襲擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:23:09.24,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖！索尼婭追擊阿莉雅的執著！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:23:09.24,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士狂熱！瑪爾斯的重大演說！！
